        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20355249/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20355249/" class="">第147页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57908794/" class=" " title="其橙">其橙</a>
                (2012.06.22)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20355249">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">空军有句术语 请注意六点钟方向</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-08-14 10:37</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
